                    <p>Monitor vital signs, track appointments, view prescriptions, and access complete pregnancy timeline in one place.</p>
                    <div class="feature-bottom-border"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-decoration"></div>
                    <div class="feature-icon gradient-blue">
                        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2">
                            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" />
                            <path d="M8 2v4M16 2v4M3 10h18M8 14h.01M12 14h.01M16 14h.01M8 18h.01M12 18h.01M16 18h.01" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Appointment Management</h3>
                    <p>Easy booking system for patients and flexible scheduling tools for clinics to manage doctor availability.</p>
                    <div class="feature-bottom-border"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-decoration"></div>
                    <div class="feature-icon gradient-purple">
                        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" />
                        </svg>
