                    </div>
                    <h3>Improved Health Outcomes</h3>
                    <p>Early detection and continuous monitoring lead to better maternal health</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Time Efficiency</h3>
                    <p>Streamlined processes save time for both patients and healthcare providers</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Better Communication</h3>
                    <p>Seamless connection between patients, doctors, and clinic staff</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10" />
                            <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4" />
                            <line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Data-Driven Decisions</h3>
                    <p>AI-powered insights help healthcare providers make informed decisions</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                            <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12" />
                            <path d="M12 2a15 15 0 0 1 0 20a15 15 0 0 1 0-20z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Accessibility</h3>
                    <p>Access your health information anytime, anywhere from any device</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card">
                    <div class="benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3.5 9-8 10c-4.5-1-8-5-8-10V6l8-4z" />
                            <rect x="9" y="10" width="6" height="5" rx="1" />
                            <path d="M10 10V9a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v1" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Security & Privacy</h3>
                    <p>End-to-end encryption ensures your medical data stays private</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Statistics Section -->
    <section class="statistics-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number" data-target="99">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">User Satisfaction</div>
                    <div class="stat-icon">%</div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number" data-target="24">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Hours Monitoring</div>
                    <div class="stat-icon">/7</div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number" data-target="100">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Data Security</div>
                    <div class="stat-icon">%</div>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-number" data-target="3">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">User Roles</div>
                    <div class="stat-icon">+</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section id="faq" class="faq-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="section-badge pink">FAQ</span>
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    Frequently Asked
                    <span class="gradient-text">Questions</span>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>Who can use NABD - نبض?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>NABD - نبض is designed for three user groups: pregnant patients tracking their journey, healthcare providers managing patient care, and clinic assistants handling appointments and operations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>Is my medical data secure?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! We use end-to-end encryption and follow HIPAA compliance standards to ensure your medical data is completely secure and private.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>How does the AI risk detection work?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Our AI analyzes patient vitals, medical history, and pregnancy progress to detect potential risks early and alert healthcare providers for timely intervention.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>Can I access NABD - نبض on mobile devices?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely! NABD - نبض is fully responsive and optimized for mobile devices, allowing you to access your health information anytime, anywhere.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>How do I book an appointment?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Simply log into your patient dashboard, view available doctors and time slots, and book your appointment with just a few clicks. You'll receive instant confirmation and reminders.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-bg">
            <div class="cta-blob cta-blob-1"></div>
            <div class="cta-blob cta-blob-2"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Transform Maternal Care?</h2>
                <p class="cta-description">
                    Join us in building a healthier future for mothers and babies
                </p>
                <button class="btn-primary btn-large" onclick="window.location.href='@Url.Action("Login", "Account")'">
                    <span>Get Started Today</span>
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <p class="cta-note">A graduation project by dedicated healthcare technology students</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-brand">
                    <div class="logo">
